@@dWARLOCK@@W

Warlocks are hexblades and curse-weavers, blending shadowcraft with precision
strikes to convert attrition into sudden collapse.

@@dPassive class advantages@@W
  * @@wExtra attack round@@W while Warlock remort is active.
  * @@wSpell critical chance@@W bonus (+0.075% per level, up to +7.5% at 100).
  * @@wCritical chance@@W bonus (+0.0375% per level, up to +3.75% at 100).
  * @@wCritical damage@@W bonus (+0.15% per level, up to +15% at 100).
  * @@wBackstab / circle damage@@W bonus (+0.75% per level, up to +75% at 100).
  * @@wRemort non-physical damage@@W bonus (+0.375% per level, up to +37.5% at 100).

@@dUnique Warlock mechanics@@W
  * Access to @@wWarlock stance@@W (hybrid melee/caster pressure).
  * Bridges stealth burst and spell pressure toward Nightblade progression.
  * Uses @@wDexterity@@W as prime remort attribute.

@@dWarlock reincarnation bonuses@@W
  * @@wAssassin + Warlock remort reincarnations >= 20@@W unlocks
    @@wDual Wield@@W permanently.

See also: @@mremort stance assassin nightblade reincarnate@@W
